{"tid":938218,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★中港車打橫行　剷安全島掉頭　途人嚇到呆","createTime":"2018-12-12T06:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T08:21:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8f82d3531f6daba719d30a2e139986b116f2316","tid":938218,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181212/photo/bkn-20181212131206800-1212_00822_001_01b.jpg?20181212143610\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181212%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181212131206800-1212_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20181212143610&h=2591f408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行人即使跟足交通燈號過路，都要打醒精神注意路況，因為隨時遇到亂來的司機。近日灣仔有中港車為求掉頭，就上演了一幕「大地任我行」。<br />\n<br />\n從Facebook群組「香港交通突發報料區」的片段可見，星期一（10日）下午4時許，一輛中港車在灣仔軒尼詩道近史釗域道燈位的路旁轉出，打橫連切兩線，駛到右線「埋定靚位」。<br />\n<br />\n當行車燈號由綠轉黃，中港車即駛出行人過路處，右轉上安全島掉頭。當時安全島尚有途人正等待過路，顯得十分吃驚，有女士立即拉開孩子避過車輛。<br />\n<br />\n發貼者表示，事後已到附近警署報案，並引述警員當時的話︰「夠晒料，交通部見啦」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181212/bkn-20181212131206800-1212_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181212%2Fbkn-20181212131206800-1212_00822_001.html&d=3LHRZsUT7ChIVUMdJzdIt6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=ee061fb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181212/bkn-20181212131206800-1212_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0d7ffb249978d6853ccb708ebafb5699db3a24c5","tid":938218,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4f0888176d2d98745a720af3d4344ac14592ef","tid":938218,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:40:21.000Z","msg":"好在唔係藍色車牌<br />\n應該會捉（掛）"},{"pid":"4925a69eaf7ec3c1cb67d6e0dacf326f294be84e","tid":938218,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim